Why Scriptgiant’s product different from others?

Scriptgiant’s freelance clone PHP script empowers entrepreneurs and small business owners to outsource anything they think of. It is excellent software that can help a buyer to create a freelancer community marketplace today. It is a ready-made and hassle free product. The software helps a buyer to create his marketplace and start his business from the very next day. The portal works in five easy steps like:


    Post your projects in seconds

    Compare prices and choose bidders

    Create payment for the project

    Approve completed project

    Release payment to the freelancers



The software is becoming more and more popular because of its advanced and many supplementary features. We are planning and working to develop some more features in the upcoming days.



